    section
      h2 Modular Content
      p Returns a list of tabs to be shown on home page, with each tab object listing module configurations for that tab.

      article.endpoint-method
        h3 /api/:brand/modular-content?tsStart=1426727558&tsEnd=1426122758
        h3.method Method: GET
        p Get a list of tabs and modules within them for a particular brand.
        div.request
          h4 Request Parameters
          p Paramter :brand can be one of defined brand codes, e.g. 'bma', 'gf'
          p
            |DateTime range can be provided using query string:
            ul
              li tsStart=1426727558
              li tsEnd=1426122758
            |Both QS params are optional. They take UNIX timestamps (without ms) as values.
            |If tsStart is ommited current datetime will be used for that offset.
            |If tsEnd is ommited a default 3 months into the future will be used instead.

        div.response
          h4 Response example
          pre
            code
              |[
              | {
              |   "title": "Featured",
              |   "targetUri": "featured",
              |   "visible": true,
              |   "modules": [
              |     {
              |       "_id": "54e7046f5b51003c36d6db9c",
              |       "title": "My New Module",
              |       "displayOrder": -2,
              |       "showExpanded": true,
              |       "badge": "specials",
              |       "navItem": "Featured",
              |       "maxRows": 5,
              |       "__v": 2,
              |       "data": [],
              |       "dataSelection": {
              |         "selectionType": "Type",
              |         "selectionId": "442"
              |       },
              |       "footerLink": {
              |         "text": "",
              |         "url": ""
              |       },
              |       "publishToChannels": [
              |         "bma",
              |         "gf"
              |       ],
              |       "visibility": {
              |         "enabled": true,
              |         "displayFrom": "2015-02-20T09:54:04.820Z",
              |         "displayTo": "2015-02-20T09:54:04.820Z"
              |       }
              |     },
              |     ...
              |     {}
              |   ]
              | },
              | ...
              | {}
              |]

